{"tid":1535685,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"全港警員委任證核查計劃","createTime":"2019-09-03T12:39:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T14:05:58.000Z","uid":222614,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"73a356aef43316c41e709bb3be32622410da10b5","tid":1535685,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:39:46.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>全港警員委任證核查計劃</ins></span></div><br />\n鑑於近日有關警員執勤時無配帶委任證之投訴有所增加，市民若遇到懷疑冒警情況，可根據以下程序處理：<br />\n<br />\n1. Call 增援（人數最少為目標 4 倍）<br />\n1.1. 增援人數不足，執行 <span style=\"color: orange;\">D</span>，<span style=\"color: orange;\">程序完成</span><br />\n1.2. 增援人數足夠，執行程序 2<br />\n2. 跟蹤<br />\n3. 等待增援到齊，及確保周圍環境安全，上前攔截<br />\n4. 向懷疑冒警人士表明理由，然後邀請對方去一個安靜既地方<br />\n4.1. 對方合作，則帶對方到一個安靜既地方，執行程序 5<br />\n4.2. 對方不合作，執行 <span style=\"color: orange;\">A</span>，<span style=\"color: orange;\">B</span>，及 <span style=\"color: orange;\">D</span>，<span style=\"color: orange;\">程序完成</span><br />\n5. 要求對方出示委任證<br />\n5.1. 對方合作，出示委任證<br />\n5.1.1. 檢查並核實委任證<br />\n5.1.2. 委任證通過核實，執行 <span style=\"color: orange;\">A</span> 及 <span style=\"color: orange;\">C</span>，<span style=\"color: orange;\">程序完成</span><br />\n5.1.3. 委任證不通過核實，執行 <span style=\"color: orange;\">A</span>，<span style=\"color: orange;\">B</span>，及 <span style=\"color: orange;\">D</span>，<span style=\"color: orange;\">程序完成</span><br />\n5.2. 對方不合作，執行 <span style=\"color: orange;\">A</span>，<span style=\"color: orange;\">B</span>，及 <span style=\"color: orange;\">D</span>，<span style=\"color: orange;\">程序完成</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">A</span>. 影相，記錄身份及詳細資料（如適用）<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">B</span>. 使用適當武力，公民拘捕及／或合法禁固<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">C</span>. 給予警告，然後命令對方離開<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">D</span>. 離開現場"},{"pid":"06114db044682375c9b00411136740437b12dd71","tid":1535685,"uid":167883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T1